sqlQuery: SELECT part.p_brand, part.p_comment, part.p_partkey FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'JUMBO CASE';

SELECT lineitem.l_shipdate, COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON orders.o_orderkey = lineitem.l_orderkey JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN region ON nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey JOIN customer ON orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey  WHERE lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('O') GROUP BY lineitem.l_shipdate ORDER BY lineitem.l_shipdate;
SELECT orders.o_clerk, orders.o_custkey, orders.o_comment FROM orders WHERE orders.o_orderdate = '1997-04-29';

SELECT lineitem.l_shipdate, SUM(partsupp.ps_supplycost) as agg_0, MAX(partsupp.ps_partkey + lineitem.l_tax) as agg_1 FROM lineitem JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 409007.3495838723 AND lineitem.l_shipmode NOT LIKE '%SH%IP%' AND partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%special,%' AND partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 562.8707865934709 AND lineitem.l_shipdate = '1994-05-10' AND lineitem.l_quantity >= 8.877705724547678 AND (lineitem.l_shipinstruct != 'DELIVER IN PERSON' OR lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%B%ACK%') AND (lineitem.l_comment LIKE '%special%' OR lineitem.l_discount <= 0.05037769708969892) AND lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('O') AND partsupp.ps_availqty <= 1059.5589127304534 AND lineitem.l_commitdate != '1994-11-10' AND (lineitem.l_partkey <= 1296363.2156232921 OR lineitem.l_partkey >= 9400303.544153476) AND lineitem.l_returnflag = 'N' AND (lineitem.l_extendedprice <= 9700.79102504188 OR lineitem.l_discount <= 0.015450240458137348 OR lineitem.l_extendedprice <= 14562.465257830938) AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 18157031.72594034 AND lineitem.l_linenumber <= 2.0 AND lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1994-07-02' GROUP BY lineitem.l_shipdate ORDER BY lineitem.l_shipdate;
SELECT orders.o_comment, orders.o_orderpriority, orders.o_orderstatus FROM orders WHERE orders.o_orderdate = '1997-06-23';

SELECT lineitem.l_shipmode, lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_shipinstruct FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_shipdate = '1992-02-21';
SELECT part.p_container, part.p_partkey, part.p_type FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'JUMBO PACK';

SELECT part.p_mfgr, AVG(region.r_regionkey) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN region ON nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey  WHERE part.p_size >= 6.660240984480664 AND region.r_comment NOT LIKE '%even%' AND (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= 647.8094927304971 OR partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 108.29967593143618 OR partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 258.5748313709098) GROUP BY part.p_mfgr ORDER BY part.p_mfgr LIMIT 10;

SELECT lineitem.l_linestatus, lineitem.l_receiptdate, lineitem.l_shipdate, SUM(orders.o_orderkey) as agg_0, SUM(lineitem.l_orderkey + lineitem.l_linenumber) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON orders.o_orderkey = lineitem.l_orderkey JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN customer ON orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey  WHERE customer.c_mktsegment LIKE '%MAC%HINERY%' AND partsupp.ps_availqty <= 9603.371722709175 AND orders.o_orderstatus IN ('F', 'P') AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 321140.0957797292 AND lineitem.l_comment LIKE '%platelets%' AND customer.c_mktsegment IN ('HOUSEHOLD', 'AUTOMOBILE', 'FURNITURE', 'BUILDING', 'MACHINERY') AND (partsupp.ps_partkey >= 4412527.151437324 OR partsupp.ps_partkey >= 6678852.168425348) AND lineitem.l_returnflag IN ('R', 'A') AND part.p_container IN ('WRAP BAG', 'MED CAN', 'WRAP DRUM', 'LG JAR', 'LG PACK', 'SM CASE', 'JUMBO CAN') AND orders.o_orderdate = '1992-12-02' AND (customer.c_custkey <= 8188835.4801844545 OR customer.c_nationkey <= 2.47053477480464) AND lineitem.l_linestatus = 'O' GROUP BY lineitem.l_linestatus, lineitem.l_receiptdate, lineitem.l_shipdate ORDER BY lineitem.l_linestatus, lineitem.l_receiptdate, lineitem.l_shipdate;

SELECT lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_linestatus, SUM(orders.o_shippriority + customer.c_custkey) as agg_0, MAX(lineitem.l_suppkey + lineitem.l_quantity) as agg_1, MIN(orders.o_custkey) as agg_2 FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey JOIN customer ON orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey  WHERE lineitem.l_linestatus = 'O' AND (orders.o_comment LIKE '%bean%s%' OR orders.o_orderkey >= 294935477.84484327) AND lineitem.l_quantity <= 41.65342660835797 AND orders.o_orderdate != '1994-11-23' AND customer.c_mktsegment IN ('FURNITURE', 'HOUSEHOLD', 'MACHINERY', 'AUTOMOBILE', 'BUILDING') AND lineitem.l_returnflag IN ('A') AND customer.c_acctbal <= 6018.457101767166 AND customer.c_mktsegment IN ('AUTOMOBILE', 'HOUSEHOLD') AND (customer.c_custkey >= 6492514.823528978 OR customer.c_custkey >= 1121158.077425618) AND orders.o_orderstatus IN ('P') AND lineitem.l_orderkey >= 347033615.8060096 AND lineitem.l_shipmode = 'FOB' AND customer.c_nationkey >= 7.5283605884651426 AND orders.o_orderpriority NOT LIKE '%5-%LOW%' GROUP BY lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_linestatus ORDER BY lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_linestatus LIMIT 10;

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, AVG(lineitem.l_discount + orders.o_shippriority) as agg_1, MIN(orders.o_custkey + lineitem.l_quantity) as agg_2 FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey  WHERE (orders.o_orderkey <= 150582408.0802354 OR orders.o_orderstatus = 'O') AND orders.o_comment LIKE '%final%,%' AND lineitem.l_returnflag IN ('A', 'N') AND lineitem.l_extendedprice >= 11144.96611179661 AND orders.o_orderpriority LIKE '%2%-HIGH%' AND lineitem.l_shipmode LIKE '%RAI%L%' AND (lineitem.l_commitdate != '1995-06-17' OR lineitem.l_quantity <= 13.551822421171098) AND lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1998-09-07' AND lineitem.l_shipmode LIKE '%SHIP%' AND lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('F') AND lineitem.l_linenumber >= 3.8523465548535 AND lineitem.l_suppkey <= 860477.7743544268 AND (orders.o_orderpriority = '2-HIGH' OR orders.o_orderpriority != '3-MEDIUM' OR orders.o_orderpriority = '1-URGENT') AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%PE%RSON%' AND orders.o_shippriority >= 0.0 HAVING MIN(orders.o_custkey + lineitem.l_quantity) >= 7500474.910074495;

SELECT orders.o_comment, orders.o_totalprice, orders.o_orderpriority FROM orders WHERE orders.o_orderdate = '1995-04-26';

SELECT part.p_container, lineitem.l_shipmode, COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM partsupp JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN region ON nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey JOIN customer ON orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey  WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate != '1992-10-14' AND supplier.s_comment NOT LIKE '%platelet%s.%' AND lineitem.l_suppkey <= 548427.9549023984 AND partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%aga%inst%' AND (nation.n_nationkey <= 0.7472379498984455 OR (nation.n_nationkey <= 15.443642272692685 AND nation.n_nationkey >= 22.51128453059002)) AND nation.n_name = 'GERMANY' AND customer.c_mktsegment != 'HOUSEHOLD' AND nation.n_regionkey <= 2.5132555516324753 AND part.p_retailprice >= 1172.3568851503971 AND customer.c_comment NOT LIKE '%platel%ets.%' AND part.p_brand != 'Brand#32' AND part.p_partkey >= 13633311.874719135 AND lineitem.l_extendedprice >= 49204.359328575854 AND lineitem.l_shipdate = '1992-07-30' AND nation.n_name LIKE '%UNITED%' AND region.r_regionkey <= 3.8278799005455877 GROUP BY part.p_container, lineitem.l_shipmode ORDER BY part.p_container, lineitem.l_shipmode LIMIT 10;

SELECT lineitem.l_linestatus, MIN(orders.o_totalprice + supplier.s_suppkey) as agg_0 FROM partsupp JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_comment NOT LIKE '%blithely.%' AND lineitem.l_suppkey >= 944861.2110020346 AND supplier.s_nationkey >= 4.917450753797709 AND lineitem.l_shipmode = 'AIR' AND orders.o_comment LIKE '%u%se%' AND nation.n_name NOT LIKE '%U%NITED%' GROUP BY lineitem.l_linestatus ORDER BY lineitem.l_linestatus;

SELECT lineitem.l_shipmode, region.r_name, MAX(partsupp.ps_availqty) as agg_0 FROM region JOIN nation ON region.r_regionkey = nation.n_regionkey JOIN supplier ON nation.n_nationkey = supplier.s_nationkey JOIN partsupp ON supplier.s_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%nod%' AND region.r_comment NOT LIKE '%bl%ithely%' AND nation.n_comment NOT LIKE '%sil%ent%' AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 10683480.554435972 AND nation.n_nationkey <= 0.23682818801719513 AND lineitem.l_extendedprice <= 57844.530893554525 GROUP BY lineitem.l_shipmode, region.r_name ORDER BY lineitem.l_shipmode, region.r_name;

SELECT part.p_container, MIN(part.p_partkey + supplier.s_suppkey) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON orders.o_orderkey = lineitem.l_orderkey JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN customer ON orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN region ON nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey  WHERE nation.n_name LIKE '%UNITED%' AND lineitem.l_shipdate = '1996-12-07' AND region.r_regionkey >= 1.1509127268224253 AND part.p_container LIKE '%CAS%E%' AND orders.o_orderstatus IN ('O', 'F', 'P') AND customer.c_mktsegment IN ('HOUSEHOLD', 'FURNITURE') AND part.p_retailprice <= 1102.4664543966244 AND partsupp.ps_availqty >= 1750.1398695958665 AND (lineitem.l_comment NOT LIKE '%f%oxes.%' OR lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('O')) AND nation.n_comment IN ('s. ironic, unusual asymptotes wake blithely r', 'l platelets. regular accounts x-ray: unusual, regular acco', 'eans boost carefully special requests. accounts are. carefull', 'y final packages. slow foxes cajole quickly. quickly silent platelets breach ironic accounts. unusual pinto be', 'nic deposits boost atop the quickly final requests? quickly regula') AND nation.n_nationkey <= 5.269362029256352 AND customer.c_custkey <= 11314901.237600654 AND supplier.s_suppkey >= 646000.4215682778 AND customer.c_comment LIKE '%ac%counts.%' AND orders.o_orderstatus = 'O' AND nation.n_name NOT LIKE '%UNITED%' AND orders.o_orderpriority LIKE '%5-L%OW%' AND lineitem.l_quantity <= 44.999682696385264 AND lineitem.l_discount <= 0.08828307259365184 GROUP BY part.p_container ORDER BY part.p_container;

SELECT part.p_container, COUNT(*) as agg_0, AVG(customer.c_custkey + part.p_partkey) as agg_1, MIN(part.p_retailprice + region.r_regionkey) as agg_2 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN region ON nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey JOIN customer ON orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey  WHERE (customer.c_mktsegment != 'FURNITURE' OR customer.c_mktsegment = 'MACHINERY' OR customer.c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE') AND region.r_comment LIKE '%requests.%' AND nation.n_regionkey <= 0.0 AND supplier.s_acctbal >= 7205.587687202361 AND region.r_regionkey <= 3.457874171130414 AND nation.n_name = 'ALGERIA' AND customer.c_custkey >= 14954814.613123443 AND part.p_container LIKE '%L%G%' GROUP BY part.p_container ORDER BY part.p_container;

SELECT orders.o_orderpriority, SUM(orders.o_totalprice) as agg_0, SUM(partsupp.ps_suppkey + lineitem.l_extendedprice) as agg_1, MIN(lineitem.l_suppkey) as agg_2 FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN customer ON orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_availqty <= 7336.339853088645 AND partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 62912.516120206936 AND customer.c_nationkey >= 15.77718270258785 AND customer.c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' AND (lineitem.l_quantity <= 19.64364348789462 OR lineitem.l_quantity >= 1.8218580299367182) AND orders.o_orderstatus != 'F' AND customer.c_comment NOT LIKE '%beans%' AND lineitem.l_commitdate != '1997-07-22' AND lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('O') AND orders.o_totalprice >= 226282.68549379756 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%NONE%' AND (partsupp.ps_partkey >= 11400826.707501862 OR partsupp.ps_partkey <= 6214225.806681894) AND orders.o_orderstatus = 'O' AND lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1996-01-20' AND partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 643.8080722445153 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%BAC%K%' AND lineitem.l_returnflag = 'R' AND customer.c_acctbal <= 4856.561529451145 GROUP BY orders.o_orderpriority HAVING SUM(partsupp.ps_suppkey + lineitem.l_extendedprice) != 538237.2044530609 ORDER BY orders.o_orderpriority;

SELECT SUM(lineitem.l_discount + lineitem.l_tax) as agg_0, SUM(partsupp.ps_availqty) as agg_1, AVG(lineitem.l_partkey) as agg_2 FROM partsupp JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey  WHERE lineitem.l_shipdate = '1997-07-17' AND lineitem.l_quantity <= 44.165880129040275 AND lineitem.l_discount <= 0.0750354542812635 AND (partsupp.ps_partkey >= 15817247.422681855 OR (partsupp.ps_availqty >= 7577.832157833943 AND partsupp.ps_partkey >= 6982899.705316764)) AND lineitem.l_returnflag != 'R' AND lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('F');

SELECT region.r_comment, MAX(orders.o_orderkey + lineitem.l_tax) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM nation JOIN region ON nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey JOIN supplier ON nation.n_nationkey = supplier.s_nationkey JOIN partsupp ON supplier.s_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey JOIN customer ON orders.o_custkey = customer.c_custkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_comment NOT LIKE '%dogged%' AND orders.o_orderstatus IN ('F') AND customer.c_mktsegment LIKE '%M%ACHINERY%' AND nation.n_regionkey >= 1.19369970155081 AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 777757.2501449451 AND customer.c_comment LIKE '%theodolites%' AND customer.c_nationkey <= 1.324727417586798 AND partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 277.87166156093275 AND orders.o_orderpriority NOT LIKE '%4-NOT%' AND region.r_name = 'MIDDLE EAST' AND nation.n_name = 'ARGENTINA' GROUP BY region.r_comment ORDER BY region.r_comment;
SELECT part.p_mfgr, part.p_name, part.p_partkey FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'LG CASE';
SELECT part.p_mfgr, part.p_partkey, part.p_comment FROM part WHERE part.p_type = 'STANDARD PLATED COPPER';

SELECT AVG(supplier.s_acctbal + part.p_partkey) as agg_0, MAX(lineitem.l_quantity + part.p_partkey) as agg_1, AVG(supplier.s_suppkey + nation.n_nationkey) as agg_2 FROM region JOIN nation ON region.r_regionkey = nation.n_regionkey JOIN supplier ON nation.n_nationkey = supplier.s_nationkey JOIN partsupp ON supplier.s_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey  WHERE part.p_name LIKE '%salmon%' AND (region.r_name = 'AMERICA' OR region.r_comment NOT LIKE '%regul%ar%');
SELECT part.p_retailprice, part.p_name, part.p_mfgr FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'SM BOX';
SELECT lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_suppkey, lineitem.l_discount FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_commitdate = '1994-09-08';
SELECT lineitem.l_receiptdate, lineitem.l_partkey, lineitem.l_suppkey FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1993-12-16';

SELECT lineitem.l_receiptdate, nation.n_name, AVG(lineitem.l_linenumber) as agg_0, MAX(region.r_regionkey) as agg_1, SUM(lineitem.l_extendedprice) as agg_2 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN region ON nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_availqty >= 7455.8929543949225 AND partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%na%g%' AND nation.n_nationkey <= 1.0849002554966964 AND nation.n_name LIKE '%UNITED%' AND part.p_container LIKE '%PACK%' AND orders.o_shippriority <= 0.0 AND part.p_partkey >= 15862496.917732382 AND (lineitem.l_returnflag IN ('N') OR lineitem.l_returnflag IN ('N', 'R', 'A') OR lineitem.l_returnflag != 'N') AND region.r_comment = 'ly final courts cajole furiously final excuse' AND lineitem.l_shipmode IN ('MAIL') AND lineitem.l_suppkey >= 287420.1164665198 AND nation.n_name != 'UNITED STATES' AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct != 'TAKE BACK RETURN' AND lineitem.l_orderkey >= 264417118.71244127 AND lineitem.l_commitdate != '1998-07-16' AND nation.n_comment LIKE '%final%' AND supplier.s_suppkey >= 283345.5205592008 GROUP BY lineitem.l_receiptdate, nation.n_name ORDER BY lineitem.l_receiptdate, nation.n_name;
SELECT part.p_name, part.p_container, part.p_mfgr FROM part WHERE part.p_brand = 'Brand#32';
SELECT lineitem.l_suppkey, lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1997-11-06';

SELECT lineitem.l_commitdate, nation.n_comment, orders.o_orderdate, MIN(partsupp.ps_supplycost + supplier.s_acctbal) as agg_0, MAX(lineitem.l_suppkey + lineitem.l_extendedprice) as agg_1, MIN(supplier.s_acctbal) as agg_2 FROM partsupp JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey  WHERE orders.o_orderpriority NOT LIKE '%5-LOW%' AND part.p_mfgr IN ('Manufacturer#3', 'Manufacturer#4', 'Manufacturer#5', 'Manufacturer#1') AND lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('F', 'O') AND (nation.n_comment LIKE '%wake%' OR nation.n_name NOT LIKE '%UNITED%') AND (part.p_partkey <= 10632430.783046884 OR (part.p_partkey >= 678470.3689830328 AND part.p_partkey >= 19816467.44475423)) AND partsupp.ps_availqty <= 4214.836808217469 AND (part.p_type IN ('SMALL POLISHED STEEL', 'MEDIUM BRUSHED COPPER', 'STANDARD ANODIZED COPPER', 'MEDIUM BRUSHED STEEL', 'LARGE BURNISHED BRASS', 'MEDIUM ANODIZED TIN', 'STANDARD POLISHED COPPER', 'STANDARD BURNISHED BRASS', 'MEDIUM POLISHED BRASS', 'LARGE POLISHED COPPER') OR part.p_brand IN ('Brand#23')) AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 17822794.730571117 AND nation.n_comment = 'rns. blithely bold courts among the closely regular packages use furiously bold platelets?' AND partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 78109.11926626168 AND part.p_type IN ('STANDARD ANODIZED STEEL', 'ECONOMY POLISHED TIN', 'ECONOMY POLISHED COPPER', 'MEDIUM PLATED STEEL', 'PROMO PLATED NICKEL', 'SMALL POLISHED BRASS') AND supplier.s_suppkey <= 122155.93107360892 GROUP BY lineitem.l_commitdate, nation.n_comment, orders.o_orderdate ORDER BY lineitem.l_commitdate, nation.n_comment, orders.o_orderdate;
SELECT lineitem.l_returnflag, lineitem.l_partkey, lineitem.l_comment FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_commitdate = '1992-01-31';

SELECT customer.c_mktsegment, AVG(customer.c_nationkey + customer.c_acctbal) as agg_0 FROM customer  WHERE customer.c_nationkey >= 3.2342119964034586 AND customer.c_custkey >= 8524064.063569989 AND customer.c_mktsegment LIKE '%BUILD%ING%' AND customer.c_acctbal <= 9222.463736095116 GROUP BY customer.c_mktsegment ORDER BY customer.c_mktsegment;
SELECT part.p_brand, part.p_mfgr, part.p_name FROM part WHERE part.p_brand = 'Brand#43';
SELECT lineitem.l_linestatus, lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_suppkey FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_shipdate = '1992-05-04';
SELECT lineitem.l_quantity, lineitem.l_suppkey, lineitem.l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE lineitem.l_commitdate = '1997-10-25';
SELECT part.p_container, part.p_size, part.p_mfgr FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'JUMBO PKG';

SELECT lineitem.l_receiptdate, lineitem.l_shipinstruct, lineitem.l_returnflag, MIN(partsupp.ps_supplycost + partsupp.ps_partkey) as agg_0, AVG(lineitem.l_orderkey + partsupp.ps_suppkey) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM lineitem JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey  WHERE lineitem.l_partkey <= 19584523.78372154 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%B%ACK%' AND lineitem.l_linenumber >= 2.0 AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 404662.8194279011 AND lineitem.l_shipmode = 'TRUCK' AND lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('F') AND lineitem.l_suppkey >= 195959.46272225416 AND lineitem.l_commitdate = '1996-10-30' AND lineitem.l_tax <= 0.0 GROUP BY lineitem.l_receiptdate, lineitem.l_shipinstruct, lineitem.l_returnflag HAVING COUNT(*) != 0 ORDER BY lineitem.l_receiptdate, lineitem.l_shipinstruct, lineitem.l_returnflag LIMIT 10;

SELECT customer.c_mktsegment, orders.o_orderdate, orders.o_orderpriority, AVG(orders.o_custkey) as agg_0, MAX(orders.o_shippriority) as agg_1 FROM customer JOIN orders ON customer.c_custkey = orders.o_custkey  WHERE customer.c_nationkey >= 18.954238651831385 AND (orders.o_orderstatus IN ('P') OR orders.o_totalprice >= 170545.02262715143 OR orders.o_orderstatus IN ('F', 'O', 'P')) AND orders.o_orderpriority = '4-NOT SPECIFIED' AND orders.o_custkey <= 1057320.5094240827 AND orders.o_orderstatus IN ('P', 'F', 'O') AND customer.c_mktsegment != 'FURNITURE' AND customer.c_acctbal <= 5948.94808472552 AND (customer.c_mktsegment NOT LIKE '%MACH%INERY%' OR customer.c_mktsegment IN ('HOUSEHOLD', 'AUTOMOBILE', 'FURNITURE', 'BUILDING') OR customer.c_mktsegment = 'FURNITURE') AND orders.o_orderkey <= 585914178.215609 GROUP BY customer.c_mktsegment, orders.o_orderdate, orders.o_orderpriority ORDER BY customer.c_mktsegment, orders.o_orderdate, orders.o_orderpriority;

SELECT part.p_container, MAX(lineitem.l_suppkey) as agg_0 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey JOIN supplier ON partsupp.ps_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey JOIN nation ON supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey JOIN region ON nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey  WHERE part.p_container NOT LIKE '%BOX%' AND region.r_regionkey <= 2.552659774424643 AND supplier.s_suppkey >= 918877.8037580029 AND supplier.s_acctbal >= 987.7182077772419 AND supplier.s_nationkey >= 2.5274622878932043 GROUP BY part.p_container ORDER BY part.p_container;

SELECT MIN(lineitem.l_extendedprice) as agg_0 FROM lineitem  WHERE lineitem.l_returnflag != 'N' AND lineitem.l_quantity >= 10.167647318523374 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct = 'NONE' AND lineitem.l_commitdate = '1998-02-22' AND lineitem.l_extendedprice >= 35728.94831701818 AND lineitem.l_orderkey >= 378030510.3663596 AND lineitem.l_shipmode NOT LIKE '%FOB%' AND lineitem.l_suppkey >= 974748.8434323814 AND lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('F');
SELECT part.p_brand, part.p_comment, part.p_name FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'SM PKG';
SELECT part.p_comment, part.p_mfgr, part.p_partkey FROM part WHERE part.p_container = 'WRAP BOX';
